## Available Scripts

All scripts support:
- `--help` - Show usage and examples
- `--profile` - Use specific configuration profile
- `--output` - Output format (text, json)

### list_{{resource}}.py

List all resources with optional filtering.

```bash
python list_{{resource}}.py [OPTIONS]

Options:
  --filter FILTER     Filter expression
  --limit N           Maximum results (default: 50)
  --output FORMAT     Output format: text, json
  --profile PROFILE   Configuration profile
```

### get_{{resource}}.py

Get details of a specific resource.

```bash
python get_{{resource}}.py ID [OPTIONS]

Arguments:
  ID                  Resource ID or key

Options:
  --output FORMAT     Output format: text, json
  --profile PROFILE   Configuration profile
```

### create_{{resource}}.py

Create a new resource.

```bash
python create_{{resource}}.py [OPTIONS]

Options:
  --name NAME         Resource name (required)
  --description DESC  Resource description
  --output FORMAT     Output format: text, json
  --profile PROFILE   Configuration profile
```

### update_{{resource}}.py

Update an existing resource.

```bash
python update_{{resource}}.py ID [OPTIONS]

Arguments:
  ID                  Resource ID or key

Options:
  --name NAME         New name
  --description DESC  New description
  --output FORMAT     Output format: text, json
  --profile PROFILE   Configuration profile
```

### delete_{{resource}}.py

Delete a resource.

```bash
python delete_{{resource}}.py ID [OPTIONS]

Arguments:
  ID                  Resource ID or key

Options:
  --dry-run           Preview deletion without executing
  --force             Skip confirmation prompt
  --profile PROFILE   Configuration profile
```

