## Common Patterns

### Batch Operations

```bash
# List and process
for id in $(python list_{{resource}}.py --output json | jq -r '.[].id'); do
    python update_{{resource}}.py $id --status "archived"
done
```

### Using with Profiles

```bash
# Development environment
python list_{{resource}}.py --profile development

# Production environment
python list_{{resource}}.py --profile production
```

### JSON Output for Scripting

```bash
# Get as JSON and filter with jq
python get_{{resource}}.py ID --output json | jq '.name'

# List and filter
python list_{{resource}}.py --output json | jq '.[] | select(.status == "active")'
```

