## Error Handling

| Error | Cause | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| 401 Unauthorized | Invalid or expired token | Check API token configuration |
| 403 Forbidden | Insufficient permissions | Verify account has required access |
| 404 Not Found | Resource doesn't exist | Check ID/key is correct |
| 429 Rate Limited | Too many requests | Wait and retry |

